{"tid":1964880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PK Tang : 7.21已檢控7人證黨衛軍公正嚴明","createTime":"2020-04-09T06:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-09T06:46:33.000Z","uid":21470,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"e0844f8fc1940a0867e99128e676dae197aff555","tid":1964880,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:33:40.000Z","msg":"鄧炳強：警方不偏不倚7.21事件亦有拘白衣人<br />\n09.04.2020 14:00<br />\n<br />\n警務處長鄧炳強出席立法會特別財委會時說，本地近日出現恐怖主義行為，例如發現有人使用爆炸品，針對脅迫政府、警方及公眾。保安局長李家超亦說，恐怖主義有在本港萌芽的跡象，甚至有人會講明要脅迫政府在政策上妥協。另外，鄧炳強回應議員提出警員執法不公時，主動提及7.21元朗暴力襲擊事件，有穿白衫的人衝入車箱打人，警方予以譴責，事後亦拘捕了37人，檢控7人，強調警方執法不偏不倚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279745&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1279745%26csid%3D261_341&d=5ySQsq589lR7QRkangxGbnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=783e7eab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1279745&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"61958089f54f004f3fcc9a11aba4c484daded886","tid":1964880,"uid":1550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:34:50.000Z","msg":"7個咁撚多呀屌你老母"},{"pid":"d2d0a4e839e0f9e8e1c26a803a018e98577aa824","tid":1964880,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:37:45.000Z","msg":"當晚700人都有，你咬得果7個你就唔好提啦好撚心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df098e9ec3f859cdaec4dfde6efd29072f244cc3","tid":1964880,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:38:10.000Z","msg":"果7個係咪冇送老婆同女去PK仔度侍寢呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"247f9ac06d33a8bf9df7bfc350c7fd0eb6361bdc","tid":1964880,"uid":229633,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T06:38:48.000Z","msg":"佢拉哂又點<br />\n個晚都係冇做野<br />\n證明條撚"},{"pid":"06a142efc76d6b551e9c98f104d5ef66c5471495","tid":